data.title: Primary Business Contacts Definition
data.meta_description: Define Primary Business Contacts. means all of the following individuals or their designees: Xxxxx Xxxxxxx for Quigo, Xxxxx Xxxx for Time, and for each Publisher shall be designated in the Enrollment Form.
data.text: In the event that the Primary Business Contacts are unable to agree upon a mutually agreeable resolution during the Discussion Period, the non-breaching party may terminate immediately after the end of the Discussion Period by providing the breaching party with written notice; and (iii) in the event that the Grievous Breach described in item (i) continues to occur during the Discussion Period, the non-breaching party may terminate immediately upon written notice to the breaching party.
